subdefinitions.definition: A locality and ghost town in British Columbia , Canada .
A village and civil parish in North Yorkshire , England , previously in Richmondshire district ( OS grid ref SD9390 ) .

A number of places in the United States : A city , the county seat of Decatur County , Georgia . A township in Schuyler County , Illinois . A township in Dubois County , Indiana . A town in Putnam County , Indiana . A township in Berrien County , Michigan . A town and village therein, in Chenango County , New York . A township and census-designated place therein, in Geauga County , Ohio . A village in Ross County , Ohio . A census-designated place in Conoy Township, Lancaster County , Pennsylvania .

definitions.definition: A habitational surname from Old English .
